when we attain Self-knowledge we will realize that non-duality (advaita) is=
 always the sole truth,both during the time of our seeming ignorance (when =
nonduality appears to be lost and duality appears to prevail) and after our=

 =E2=80=98attaining=E2=80=99 Self, the non-dual reality.

